Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Relationship advice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes! Right now,\NI'm facing a major problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}MIYUKI SHIROGANE\NWANTS TO WORK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I thought only you, the Love Master,\Nwould be able to solve this issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The ship has already sailed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll see your voyage through to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we go again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm at the end of my rope\Nfor this charade!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}How could I ever be thought of\Nas the Love Master?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}How did I qualify for that title?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}If a virgin can qualify,\NI'll get it sooner or later!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The idea of me giving\Ngirlfriend advice is ridiculous!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, make this an easy one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}That's Miss Kashiwagi's boyfriend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I thought things were going well with them\Ndoing the charity work together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right. Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to hold\NMiss Kashiwagi's hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BLURT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}We've been dating for a month now,\Nso I'd like to do something romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's why I want your advice\Non what I should do to hold hands with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why don't you ask a friend for advice?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't this just bragging?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he come to brag,\Npretending he wants advice?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The president has a big heart,\Nbut I'm sure even he'll get mad at—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}OH-THAT-ISM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The face of a Buddha?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He brought up something normal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even I can advise about holding hands.\NI can handle the ABCs of love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ABCs of love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of the many kinds of couples,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}the meaning between them differs\Ndepending upon the depth of the relationship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ABCs are one barometer\Nto measure that depth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A is kissing. B is petting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}C indicates a relationship\Nthat has gone all the way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}This boyfriend is a beginner who decided\Nto begin climbing the ABC mountain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}The stage he is at differs little\Nfrom fellow virgin, Shirogane.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen. Holding hands is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rent a cruiser, and as you gaze\Nat the sun sinking below the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,let your fingertips accidentally\Non purpose brush up against hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When she looks embarrassed,\Nsmile and take her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a tall order!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess that's the kind of person\Nthe president is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I don't have the money to rent a cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,get a part-time job!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A job?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:04:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You work up a sweat. I swear, afterwards,\Nthe taste of the water from the fountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,is as good as cola! I guarantee it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why not just drink cola?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The president's workaholism\Nmight be coloring this argument.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm not saying you need\Nto rent a luxury liner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can rent a small one\Nfor 10,000 or 20,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But you need to have a license\Nto pilot a boat, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A small boat license is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's easy to get, so I recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's got one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,W-Wow! I'm impressed, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can get one by taking a three-day course,\Nand it costs less than 100,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But 100,000 yen is a lot of money to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So get a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Why do you try to keep pushing him\Ninto the workforce?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Certainly, you're describing a great situation,\Nbut I've got a fundamental problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My hands get all sweaty\Nwhen I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm afraid to take Miss Kashiwagi's hand\Nwhen mine is slick with sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}you have palmar hyperhidrosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}PALMAR HYPERHIDROSIS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't know what that is,\Nbut you're probably right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Don't make a diagnosis\Nbefore seeing a doctor!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That would require surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Surgery for hyperhidrosis\Nruns about 100,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Get a job! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TODAY
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}OGASAWARA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}OKINAWA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you obsessed\Nwith making him work?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be more constructive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,to have a sweaty forehead from work\Nthan sweaty hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was a pretty good line!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That decides it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}For holding hands,\Na part-time job is essential!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Wrong! It isn't essential at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As it happens, the place where I work\Nis looking for people for summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shall I inquire on your behalf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't worry. I'd be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's physical labor. It's tough at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'd be there every step of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, realize your basic mistake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}President!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The cost of the boat, license and surgery...\NWe're looking at about 200,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The job pays 1,000 yen an hour,\Nso 5,000 yen for a five-hour shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you work 40 days,\Nyou should be able to swing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You'll have a fun summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}This is bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}At this rate, the president's summer vacation\Nwill be consumed by working!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}After my trouble coming up\Nwith summer vacation plans!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}They'll all be ruined!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'll arrange an interview—\N- Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The color of her magnifying glass is pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's the color of truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Enter the Love Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}LOVE DETECTIVE CHIKA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fujiwara and Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let you\Ntalk about love without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shinomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not part of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm not a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It seems you're together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, what's the matter at hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, the question was\Nhow he can hold his girlfriend's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh? Can't he just normally\Ntake her by the hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What element is gumming up the works?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, the problematic aspect\Nis a high psychological hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sweaty palms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After my love sensor went off...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that the level\Nof male relationship advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You say it's nothing to worry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After all, the only advice here\Nis "Do your best," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Do your best"? That's so vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not vague!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's so nervous that his hands\Nget sweaty which is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And yet... And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And yet, he screws up the courage,\Ntakes her hand, and it works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be fun if you could\Ngrab her hand without any effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trying to skip the hard part\Nis a fundamental mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Reflect on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}FWISH
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was just lacking in pure will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just trying hard is enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What about the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He doesn't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Although I've never held hands\Nwith a boy myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Days later...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}On a date with Kashiwagi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}he somehow succeeded\Nin holding Kashiwagi's hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}At any rate, I'm glad I protected\Nthe president's summer vacation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}RESULTS\NOF TODAY'S MATCH:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shirogane loses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}SHIROGANE LOSES\N(FAILED TO RECRUIT A PART-TIMER)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe Shinomiya could work there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, dream on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he really needs someone\Nto work there, he should ask me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jeez, club activities suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Club activities are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}KAGUYA WANTS HIM TO JOIN IN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dedicating oneself to something\Ndevelops the body and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I know\Nthat club activities are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Without them, students would have free time\Nand go on the path of delinquency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Juvie, suspension,\Nthe breakdown of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}MOM\NSOB SOB
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In the end, they get pregnant,\Nand we do a fundraising campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Club activities are also a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,to keep mentally immature children\Nisolated from all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, yes, there's that aspect to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Club activities!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two pyramids exist at Shuchiin Academy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}One is the parentage pyramid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}DAUGHTER OF THE PRESIDENT\NOF A MAJOR SHIPBUILDING COMPANY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}SON OF A HOSPITAL\NDIRECTOR
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}99% of the students at Shuchiin Academy\Ncome from wealthy families.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}DAUGHTER OF THE PRESIDENT\NOF AN ADVERTISING AGENCY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}DAUGHTER\NOF A SHINOMIYA\NGROUP DIRECTOR
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}DAUGHTER OF\NTHE PRESIDENT\NOF A FAMOUS I.T. COMPANY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Therefore, this is\Nthe ensuing balance of power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}ALL OTHERS\N(GENERAL PUBLIC)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:38.22,LowerLeft2,NTP,0,0,0,,DOCTORS, PRESIDENTS OF\NMEDIUM-SIZED CORPORATIONS,\NPRO SPORTS ATHLETES
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}It could be called\Nthe "Social Standing Hierarchy."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS,\NEXECUTIVES OF LARGE\NCORPORATIONS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.22,LeftSignM2,NTP,0,0,0,,WORLD-FAMOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}PRIVILEGED CLASS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}SPORTS\NTABLE TENNIS\NCULTURAL\NNO CLUB\NMANGA CLUB (ANIME CLUB)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}And the other pyramid...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}The Club Caste!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyone affiliated with a sports club alone\Nmay be popular,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}regardless of actual performance\Nduring club activities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}BENCHWARMER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Students who belong to no club\Nor cultural club members...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}feel negatively about\Nthis unreasonable state of affairs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Those who are serious about it\Nare okay in my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But don't the majority put on "We're serious"\Nfaces while pretending to be best buddies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a really cold thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's like, what's fun about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They should do it\Nas if their lives depended on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wish they would all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shoot. Ishigami is off\Non one of his anti-youth rants.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get him back on topic somehow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, let's put a pin in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}About the club budget draft...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,With the recent recession,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}2019 STUDENT COUNCIL\N(CLUB SPONSORSHIP)\NTREASURY BUDGET DRAFT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,contributions are down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'll have to cut club budgets\Nwherever we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I definitely want to hear\Nyour opinion as treasurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Going from my experience\Ndoing accounting for the family business,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}NOTE: SON OF THE PRESIDENT\NOF A TOY MANUFACTURING\NCOMPANY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have to say there's a lot of waste\Nin this proposed budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We should probably slash\Nthe soccer club's budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}A lot of the members have girlfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's your reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For the same reason, let's reduce the\Nbasketball club and the baseball club's budgets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How about a 50,000 yen reduction\Nfor every couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Taxing couples?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shouldn't those who are happy\Nbe taxed the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a happiness tax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even a tyrant wouldn't tax like that!\NThat's just a total personal grudge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It is a personal grudge,\Nbut is that so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It is bad! It's really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't understand, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't understand my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Hey, you don't have a game\Nthis Sunday, do you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}It's been a while, so let's go somewhere!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Sorry. We have practice that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Lately all you do is practice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, but the tournament's coming up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm putting it all on the line for soccer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tak...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}THROB
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You burst into tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's okay with me\Nthat they have girlfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm so used to it that I don't feel\Nanything about it at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you've got a girlfriend, go on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why are you even at practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you've got a precious girlfriend,\Nwhat could be more important than her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When I have nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L-Look, you know a lot about computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everyone says the same thing to otaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe you should join one of those clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is it possible to be in a club\Nand also do student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, Shinomiya and Fujiwara do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so it's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. What clubs are they in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I believe Fujiwara belongs\Nto the tabletop game club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can imagine her enjoying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shinomiya is in the Japanese archery club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Japanese archery club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That really suits her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,With Japanese archery,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,if you've got breasts, the bowstring\Nrubs against them when you pull it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But with Shinomiya-senpai's size,\Nthere's no need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Ishigami!\N- Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Behind you! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}FWISH FWISH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}RUMBLE RUMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ishigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ishigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I hear it's possible to bind your boobs\Nwith bandages up to D cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure Fujiwara-senpai\Nis way bigger than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so the day she tried Japanese archery,\Nher chest would be knocked all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They'd be like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}WOBBLE WOBBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}RUMBLE RUMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hit the brakes, Ishigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ishigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}GRIN
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}FWAP FWAP
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're lucky, Ishigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miss Fujiwara is kind,\Nso she'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's probably the only one\Nwho'd forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}RUMBLE RUMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President, I'm going home\Nto write my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was a life full of liking\Nbig ones and small ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Were you two at your clubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}President, please increase\Nthe budget of the tabletop game club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll give you a cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}DAUGHTER OF\NA POLITICIAN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't offer me such an obvious bribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I've never been in a club,\Nso I don't know what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Then, you should join my club.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}No! If I said that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}it'd be like saying I wanted to be\Nin the same club as the president!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'm not really that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then why don't you try joining my club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tabletop game club, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:15:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}President, the budgets for the cultural clubs\Nhaven't changed much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you're there to observe\Nas a member of student council,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,then logically, the sports clubs have had\Nthe major budget changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, my club is special!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We always buy new games,\Nso it's like a money pit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That doesn't endear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My club! Please join my club!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I don't really have time\Nto join a club because of my part-time job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I like this situation.\NIt feels like I'm popular.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't tell them I can't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:37.91,LowerRight,NTP,0,0,0,,RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH:\NSHIROGANE WINS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shirogane wins.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}BECAUSE FOR A SHORT TIME,\NHE'S ABLE TO FEEL LIKE HE HAS A HAREM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I WANNA BE POPULAR.\NI WANNA BE POPULAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}PSYCHOANALYSIS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, Pesu put Father's shoe\Nin his mouth and ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Father chased after him, yelling,\N"I'm not bread from Shizuoka Prefecture!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KAGUYA WANTS TO CONTROL IT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I held my sides with laughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I love how you laugh, Miss Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-Where's that coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After all, a long time ago,\Nyou didn't even crack a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When we were in middle school,\Nthey called you "Kaguya the Ice Princess."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was like you were in your own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was like that back then, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After joining the student council, you were\Non bad terms with the president for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shirogane, would you not look at me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were looking at me first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was as comfortable\Nas sitting on thorns back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-It was like that back then, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I kept my distance from people\Nbecause I was afraid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miss Fujiwara was the only one\Nwho stayed by my side despite that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I have to treat her better.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's my dream to see you\Nroar with laughter someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wouldn't let myself\Nlose control like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but I bet you'd laugh\Nif you saw my Pesu doing tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}His wiener!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Miss Kaguya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I understand!\NYou mean your dog's trick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Perhaps you balance a hot dog on his nose,\Nand he waits for a command to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I was just shocked\Nto hear the word "wiener"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Anyway, he does the normal trick\Nlike putting one or two paws in your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}suddenly coming out of the mouth\Nof a cute girl like Miss Fujiwara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but his wiener is really weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}How can I explain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It hangs all the way to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M-Miss Kaguya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry. I choked on my tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SHIVER SHIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I laughing\Nwhen I hear the word "wiener"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dirty jokes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}EASY\NPHYSICAL EDUCATION
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}After learning from past mistakes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya has begun to study the facts of life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}HMM HMM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}However,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}regarding slang and metaphors, Kaguya's knowledge\Nis still at the level of a young grade-schooler.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But Pesu is sneaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}His wiener gets big when there's food,\Nbut otherwise, it's just a tiny stump!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}NORMAL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, right now,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SMALL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya is at the stage where kids laugh\Nat words like "wiener" and "boobs"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BIG
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}NORMAL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SMALL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BIG
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone goes through this period,\Nand Kaguya is smack-dab in the middle of it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}NORMAL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SMALL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BIG
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kaguya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}If she realizes I'm laughing\Nat a vulgar word like that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}the Shinomiya family\Nwill never live down my shame!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my dream to see you\Nroar with laughter someday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Making Miss Fujiwara's dream come true\Nwith a wiener would just be despicable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to reset my feelings!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wiener.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wiener.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}M-Miss Kaguya is roaring with laughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'm thrilled!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Fujiwara's dream came true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M-Miss Fujiwara?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You will stop, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course she wouldn't stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}WILLIE THE ELEPHANT\NNICE TO MEET YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as a parent\Nwill continue tickling their child...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wiener! Wiener! Wiener! Wiener!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}when the child demands them to stop,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}nothing could make\Nthe overjoyed Fujiwara stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}President?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen, Miss Fujiwara!\NDon't you dare do that in front of a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}GRIN
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}She's not going to stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It'll be okay. I'm a young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I could never say that word\Nin front of a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}At least not out of my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}No! There's some hidden meaning\Nto her words!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Say, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you call that little dog\Nthat looks like a sausage again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dachshund?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Wiener dog?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She intends to make\Nthe president say "wiener"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the president says that word,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I won't be able to keep myself\Nfrom laughing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let the president say "wiener"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But isn't there\Nanother weird expression for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gotta stop this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Think!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Use all of your brain cells, Kaguya Shinomiya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't it "wien"—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hot dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I heard that's what they sometimes\Ncall it in the U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's that Viennese breaded,\Npan-fried cutlet called?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Wien—\N- Schnitzel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's similar to our tonkatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's the common name for a hot dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Wie—\N- Frankfurter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The term comes from Frankfurt, Germany,\Nwhere sausages like hot dogs originated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, what else? What else?\NI can't think of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I held the fort!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Now the president won't say the word "wiener"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'm out of danger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Darn it! President, I wanted "wiener"\Nto come out of your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Every time you were about to give me "wiener,"\NMiss Kaguya would get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P-Perverts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I would never do anything like that here!\NWhat in the world are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you nymphos?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you nymphomaniacs?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wiener.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}BFFT
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Enough! Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's too funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've had enough wieners!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miss Fujiwara,\Nwhen are you going to be satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop torturing me with wieners!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miss Kaguya, your response\Njust makes me feel so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}S-Something unspeakable\Nis happening behind this door!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why don't we switch?\NYou take the wiener part!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No way! You won't see that\Ncome out of my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, like you never have before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One or two more wieners won't hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wiener!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wiener! Wiener!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fujiwara wins.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wiener!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, do you have one?
